{"tid":1143245,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美警告北極變成另一個南海　中方：顛倒黑白","createTime":"2019-05-07T15:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T02:47:22.000Z","uid":51620,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aca6800cf1def49d71a935b261d4d4ede807ea9d","tid":1143245,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/c0.9.476.249a/p476x249/60231093_450109199126755_7442583050090708992_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=c6821278adedeba1057e137441c2ec39&amp;oe=5D698368\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fc0.9.476.249a%2Fp476x249%2F60231093_450109199126755_7442583050090708992_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Dc6821278adedeba1057e137441c2ec39%26oe%3D5D698368&h=4d91180a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】北極理事會會議在芬蘭舉行，會議前夕，美國國務卿蓬佩奧批評，中國和俄羅斯在北極的活動極具野心，警告要提防北極可能會變成另一個南海。中方指摘美國的講法顛倒黑白。<br />\n<br />\n北極理事會會議在芬蘭的羅瓦涅米舉行，八個處於北極圈的成員國，包括俄羅斯和美國的外長出席，今次會議正值「極地爭奪戰」，被形容為已進入「肉搏」階段。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧在會議前夕發表的演說亦指，由於擁有石油、天然氣、礦物和豐富漁產，北極已成為大國的角力場，當地的利益正面臨新的威脅，他點名批評中國和俄羅斯在北極的行為具侵略性，更特別警告要提防北極變成另一個南海。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國自稱「近北極國家」，蓬佩奧表明，只有「北極國家」和「非北極國家」，沒有第三個類別，中國完全沒有在北極地區主張權利的資格，他又說北極雖然是蠻荒之地，但不是無法無天，美國不會坐視不理中俄的侵略行為，將加強在北極的安全和外交力量。<br />\n<br />\n以觀察員身分參加會議的中國指摘蓬佩奧的說法顛倒黑白。<br />\n<br />\n中國近年在北極非常活躍，2012至17年間於北極的投資達900億美元，去年初，發表白皮書《中國的北極政策》，自稱為「近北極國家」，首次闡述開發北極的立場和政策，積極推動「冰上絲綢之路」，希望拉攏北極圈國家，將「一帶一路」版圖擴展到北極。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=347154&amp;fbclid=IwAR2S5yqT-DZam4m9bYyFKbUzOrsghd9HLAEg_AOJJx2009_UtGk362esy98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347154%26fbclid%3DIwAR2S5yqT-DZam4m9bYyFKbUzOrsghd9HLAEg_AOJJx2009_UtGk362esy98&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SxF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=37653a21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347154%26fbclid%3DIwAR2S5yqT-DZam4m9bYyFKbUzOrsghd9HLAEg_AOJJx2009_UtGk362esy98&h=958c2dae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=347154&amp;fbclid=IwAR2S5yqT-DZam4m9bYyFKbUzOrsghd9HLAEg_AOJJx2009_UtGk362esy98</a>"},{"pid":"9ad5b3d81fff3209fbea5627d650477d239b75ed","tid":1143245,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"全球自古以來都是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e565fbe543ca1872f2aa271089a2a3ca5523182","tid":1143245,"uid":93153,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"其實真心講句<br />\n中國軍力有能力去到北極挑戰美俄？<br />\n會否講大咗少少<br />\n純好奇"},{"pid":"eae887862a3c94143768e273f2da8b044d1b6207","tid":1143245,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"屈定先冇死"},{"pid":"b0177e4fc95cf1647889a8c503ed2a969c1c1e71","tid":1143245,"uid":18012,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e565fbe543ca1872f2aa271089a2a3ca5523182","tid":1143245,"uid":93153,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"其實真心講句<br />\n中國軍力有能力去到北極挑戰美俄？<br />\n會否講大咗少少<br />\n純好奇"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯海軍其實好弱"},{"pid":"7019d6058ff0a98a9939ed2f1874074caa395a3b","tid":1143245,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b0177e4fc95cf1647889a8c503ed2a969c1c1e71","tid":1143245,"uid":18012,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e565fbe543ca1872f2aa271089a2a3ca5523182","tid":1143245,"uid":93153,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"其實真心講句<br />\n中國軍力有能力去到北極挑戰美俄？<br />\n會否講大咗少少<br />\n純好奇"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯海軍其實好弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"中俄海軍都係垃圾<b